title: List of UnNetHack tiles
data:
This page lists [tiles](/wiki/Tile "Tile") that are present in [UnNetHack](/wiki/UnNetHack "UnNetHack") but do not match any tile in vanilla [NetHack](/wiki/NetHack "NetHack"). Some of these tiles are also in other [variants](/wiki/Variant "Variant").

List of UnNetHack tiles

From NetHackWiki
Jump to navigation Jump to search

This page lists tiles that are present in UnNetHack but do not match any tile in vanilla NetHack. Some of these tiles are also in other variants.

Monsters

anti-matter vortex
Aphrodite
black marketeer
Cthulhu
disintegrator
Executioner
mugger
snow ant
uranium imp
vorpal jabberwock
wax golem

Objects

Most of these are additional randomized appearances.

iron safe
tinfoil hat
glass ring
obsidian ring
plain ring
quartz ring
convex amulet
elliptic amulet
lunate amulet
oval amulet
rectangular amulet
spiked amulet
warped amulet
icy potion
luminescent potion
muddy potion
sparkling potion
colorful spellbook
dark spellbook
faded spellbook
left-handed spellbook
long spellbook
psychedelic spellbook
spiral-bound spellbook
spotted spellbook
stapled spellbook
stylish spellbook
tartan spellbook
